Introducing recurring subscriptions! You can now subscribe to Lucidchart Basic and Lucidchart Professional on a month to month basis unlocking all the same great features as before. Plus your subscription will renew automatically with the ability to cancel anytime so no need to worry about it expiring. If you are currently on the six month plan and would like to move to a month to month subscription please email support lucidchart.com. You can always reach us at support lucidchart.com with feedback questions or issues you can also tap Get Support or Send Feedback in the app . Thanks for being a Lucidchart customer!

Improved exporting and sharing! New: Export PDF PNG Visio from the documents list! Select a document and tap the share button to access the export and share dialog. There is now an explicit share button in the editor which takes you to the export and share dialog. Tapping the document title used to show exporting and sharing options but now simply lets you rename the document. Pending invitations in the collaborator dialog now include a share button so you can re send the invitation. You can always reach us at support lucidchart.com with feedback questions or issues you can also tap Get Support or Send Feedback in the app . Thanks for being a Lucidchart customer!

This release is full of bug fixes and polish. Enjoy! You can now log in with your passwords saved in Safari Keychain. We no longer log you out every 30 days if your password hasn t changed . Improved text edit mode when using hardware keyboards more improvements coming soon! When you try to close a document with unsaved changes we now warn you to prevent accidental loss. Completely new design optimized for iOS 8 Improved sharing and collaboration: work with teammates on any browser and any device COMING SOON: Save your documents for offline viewing This is the first release of our new rewritten app. We know it s been a long time coming and we re very excited to get it into your hands! You can always reach us at support lucidchart.com with any questions or feedback and thanks for being a Lucidchart customer! We ve completely replaced the old versions of the document list and sharing functionality as well as the login and signup workflow. It s now much easier to share your documents and folders quickly find recent items and search for documents across all your whole account. We ve made several updates to the editor to make it more stable for your day to day use. Even for documents that we don t fully support on the iPad such as floorplans or certain mockups you ll be able to see and interact with a view only version of the document. We re just starting work on a brand new editor and we re working hard to get it in your hands as soon as possible. It s a big project but this new editor will have a brand new touch optimized interface to make editing even faster and more seamless. Don t worry we ll keep making improvements to the rest of the app while we work on it so you can expect the app to keep getting even better over the next weeks and months. The Lucidchart Mobile Team
